  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK756">
<l>uṟuporuḷu mulku poruḷunta ṉoṉṉārt</l>
<l>teṟuporuḷum vēntaṉ poruḷ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Unclaimed wealth, wealth acquired by taxes, and wealth (got) by conquest of foes are (all) the wealth of the king.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
